      • add

        public ExcelWorksheet add(SheetType type,
                          String worksheetName)
        Adds an empty worksheet to the end of the collection.

        If this is the first worksheet added to the collection the active worksheet is set to this worksheet.

        Parameters:
        type - The sheet type.
        worksheetName - Worksheet name.
        Returns:
        Newly created worksheet.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - Worksheet name is not unique.

      • getActiveWorksheet

        public ExcelWorksheet getActiveWorksheet()
        Gets active worksheet.

        Active worksheet is the one selected when file is opened with Microsoft Excel. By default active worksheet is the first one added with ExcelFile.addWorksheet(String), add(String) or add(SheetType, String) methods.

      • setActiveWorksheet

        public void setActiveWorksheet(ExcelWorksheet value)
        Gets active worksheet.

        Active worksheet is the one selected when file is opened with Microsoft Excel. By default active worksheet is the first one added with ExcelFile.addWorksheet(String), add(String) or add(SheetType, String) methods.

        GemBox.Spreadsheet Free allows setting active worksheet to only one of the first 5 worksheets, otherwise active worksheet defaults to the first worksheet.
